OL,3,CSam Kerr to leave Chelsea at the end
OL,4,Cof the season
OL,6,FChelsea forward Sam Kerr has announced
OL,7,Fshe will leave the club at the end of
OL,8,Fthe season when her contract expires.
OL,10,FThe Australian international has
OL,11,Fscored 115 times for Chelsea since she
OL,12,Fjoined the club in 2020, one behind
OL,13,Fthe club's all-time leading scorer,
OL,14,FFran Kirby.
OL,16,FAnnouncing her departure, Kerr said:
OL,17,F"When I reflect on my Chelsea career
OL,18,Fand doing it for the last time
OL,19,F(against Manchester United on
OL,20,FSaturday), I just feel happy.
