OL,3,CSam Kerr to leave Chelsea at the end
OL,4,Cof the season
OL,6,F"I feel so grateful to have played for
OL,7,Fthis club for six years and won as
OL,8,Fmany trophies as we could."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe 32-year-old won five WSL titles,
OL,16,Fthree FA Cups, three League Cups, and
OL,17,Fthe Community Shield during her six
OL,18,Fand a half years at the club.
