OL,3,CSam Kerr to leave Chelsea at the end
OL,4,Cof the season
OL,6,FShe was Chelsea's top scorer in the
OL,7,FWSL for the 2020/21 and 2021/22
OL,8,Fcampaigns and scored 29 goals in 38
OL,9,Fappearances in the 2022/23 season, as
OL,10,Fthe Blues went on to secure another
OL,11,FWSL and FA Cup double.
OL,13,FConsidered one of the greatest
OL,14,Fstrikers in world football, Kerr is
OL,15,FAustralia's record goalscorer, scoring
OL,16,F75 goals in 139 games since her debut
OL,17,Fin 2009, aged just 15.
